      "id": "spec:project:architecture-constraints-001",
      "type": "spec",
      "title": "GESP 分类目录优先",
      "summary": "### GESP 分类目录优先 产品必须以分类目录为主线，而不是搜索页优先；核心信息架构是 level -> algorithm domain -> problem type -> problems -> knowledge points。",
